-- Citi names Laskowski as Asia-Pac COO, PE head
-- 
-- Sun Jun 20, 2010 10:00pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2010/06/21/us-citi-laskowski-idUSTRE65K0CD20100621

 

 HONG KONG  (Reuters) - Citigroup has named Chris Laskowski as its chief operating officer (COO) and the head of financial entrepreneurs group for Asia Pacific ex-Japan, an internal memo seen by Reuters said on Monday. 

 Laskowski, who previously held the role of head of private equity banking for Citi in Asia, is returning to Hong Kong from Citi's Chicago office. (Reporting by  Denny Thomas  and  Michael Flaherty ; Editing by Jacqueline Wong)